  "about": {
    "heading": "Where Vision Meets Execution",
    "paragraphs": [
      "Founded in 2016, Framecraft Studios emerged from a simple belief: every brand, event, and moment deserves to be captured with intention and artistry. What started as a two-person operation has grown into a full-service production studio trusted by global brands and local visionaries alike.",
      "We're not just camera operators—we're storytellers, strategists, and visual architects. Our team combines technical precision with creative intuition, ensuring every frame serves a purpose. From pre-production planning to final color grading, we obsess over the details that transform good content into unforgettable experiences.",
      "Based in Los Angeles with a network spanning three continents, we've produced everything from intimate brand documentaries to large-scale event coverage. Our work has been featured in international campaigns, earned industry recognition, and most importantly, helped our clients connect with their audiences in meaningful ways."
    ],
